{"tid":1497594,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢必看！被捕後自救手冊","createTime":"2019-08-23T04:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:32:40.000Z","uid":279963,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb3ac7453168c421a0e49c0fb78b163899edb79","tid":1497594,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"李安然大律師教各位被捕後需要做嘅事情，以及解釋背後嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RvyMaYBa1hE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRvyMaYBa1hE&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1ZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=f3891183\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RvyMaYBa1hE</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 冷静，保持緘默(除左律師外，對<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人</span>都係我冇野講)<br />\n佢解釋被捕後同警察合作(提供資料) 只會為警察提供證據去指證自己。第二，警察有臥底混入示威者中，你對住其他被捕嘅，都要冇野講。第三，你屋企人來警署見你，警察係會喺旁邊聽住，所以都要冇野講。你最多只會留喺警署48小時，警察會不斷同你講你合作就可以快d走，千祈唔可以配合。<br />\n<br />\n2. 繼續唔好講野，唔好跌入警察嘅誘導式發問<br />\n你以為自己答緊一d無關嘅問題，但佢會慢慢引導你講成自己有參與非法集結/暴動。<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔好拎手提電話出來解鎖，要打畀律師/屋企人，都係用警署嘅電話去打。<br />\n喺佢冇法庭搜查令嘅情況下，絕對係唔能夠查你電話/屋企。<br />\n<br />\n段片都係17分鐘，可能你覺得係廢話，但我相信當你好緊張不安時，可能會唔記得需要做d咩野。"},{"pid":"0851fca766c045b8859df1da257d18344e7c5c10","tid":1497594,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4e0c44f0ce0f882199514427b50381515ad39e","tid":1497594,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549538c4ca8ac202efa8330c834c6c5031b3f6f5","tid":1497594,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZudLX07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudLX07.jpg&h=5fb14145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港電影欠香港人一場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497679</a>"},{"pid":"e985383cfa7f24aa0a2d351c160688bda6d3dae7","tid":1497594,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:32:40.000Z","msg":"推一推，希望可以幫到人"}]}